66
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:13,520
 Underfitting happen due to the model is too simple,

67
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:20,320
 very high regularization features are weak or missing, not enough training.

68
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:29,360
 So sometimes if you have like very few samples related to a data set,

69
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:35,360
 where the model actually can't learn the important features out of that one.

70
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,920
 So for example, everybody's coming and they say,

71
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:43,360
 I have a fever, I'm feeling back pain and so on.

72
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:50,800
