210
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,880
 I will construct the whole decision tree.

211
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:42,400
 And afterwards, I will traverse this rule over here, and then I can answer.

212
00:19:43,360 --> 00:19:53,440
 So, it means even to answer a one test case, one test sample, I need the construction of

213
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,800
 whole decision tree.

214
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:57,600
 Second thing.

215
00:19:59,440 --> 00:20:08,880
 You have mentioned after this one that if the student value is no, income value is high,

216
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:18,640
 age value is less than 30, then you will not approve the loan for that particular individual.

